title: LootLoot
description:
Loot Loot (officially LootLoot as one word) is the first in a series of arcade games to be released by Bus Gas Explosion Studios. Based on the classic game of Snake, play as an adventurer exploring ancient temple ruins and collect valuable treasure! Collecting at least 40 pieces of treasure will open up exit stairs to move onto the next level. Each new level becomes larger and more dangerous, as spiked traps and snake pits appear. As the adventurer continues the journey into the depths, more obstacles will appear to make treasure hunting harder.


Visit their Patreon atto support the indie start-up company.
Visit http://busgasexplosion.com/ for more details and to provide feedback.
Visit https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.busgasexplosion.lootlootfree for more recent updates
